{"type":null,"faqId":45385,"title":"如何升级荣耀盒子M321为最新版本？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>如果有新的软件版本，您可以进入“</span><span class=\"s1\">设置 &gt; 版本升级</span><span>”，将系统升级为最新版本。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164985\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>您还可以通过 U 盘/microSD 卡进行升级，操作方式如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>在电脑上访问 http://emui.huawei.com/plugin.php?id=hwdownload，下载最新软件版本。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>将最新软件版本压缩包名修改为 update.zip。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span>在 U 盘/microSD  卡根目录下创建的名为 dload 的目录。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 4  </span><span>将 update.zip 压缩包拷贝到 dload 的目录下。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 5  </span><span>将 U 盘/microSD  卡插入荣耀盒子M321，重启盒子。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 6  </span><span>进入主界面，等待几秒后，当弹出类似如下提示框提示升级（如图）。按遥控器 OK 键，启动升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164986\" style=\"width:4.6770835in;height:2.65625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 7  </span><span>等待升级完成（如图）。系统重启进入主界面表示升级成功。可进入“</span><span class=\"s1\">设置 &gt; 关于</span><span>”或“</span><span class=\"s1\">设置 &gt; 版本升级</span><span>”，查看当前软件版本。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164987\" style=\"width:4.6875in;height:2.6541667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 8  </span><span>升级成功后，请断开电源，拔出 U 盘/microSD 卡。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164988\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>在升级完成前，请不要移除U 盘/microSD 卡或拔掉电源。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>升级过程中如果出现断电情况，请尝试再次用U 盘/microSD 卡升级。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":251,"faqType":"版本与升级","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"906","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Software-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556900000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":56,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"升级,新版本,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}